            "title": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "jcr:createdBy": "Ashwini.PreethiP1@Site B.com",
              "jcr:title": "What's the deal?",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "Ashwini.PreethiP1@Site B.com",
              "textStyle": "tdds:text-title-2",
              "isAccessRestricted": "false",
              "colorTextSource": "default",
              "jcr:created": "Wed Aug 28 2024 19:09:22 GMT+0000",
              "type": "h2",
              "linkTarget": "_self",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Wed Aug 28 2024 19:09:22 GMT+0000",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/title",
              "colorTextPalette": "tdds:color-primary-100",
              "colorText": "color-initial",
              "textAlignment": "tdds:ta-inherit"
            },
            "table": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "jcr:createdBy": "admin",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "Alkia.Morris@Site B.com",
              "isAccessRestricted": "false",
              "jcr:created": "Mon Aug 05 2024 13:28:56 GMT+0530",
              "text": "<table cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody><tr><th width=\"20%\">Eligible channels</th>\r\n<td width=\"80%\"><ul>\r\n<li>Consumer Care</li>\r\n<li>Retail (Company-owned,&nbsp;<a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/operations/in-store/store-in-store/costco-sams-club-program.html\">Store-in-Store</a>, and Authorized Retailer)</li>\r\n<li>Samsung.com<ul>\r\n<li>Only I/R account types are supported for orders on Samsung.com&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Samsung.com orders cannot be shipped to Puerto Rico or USVI</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Micro (Care, Direct, VBS Outbound, Micro VR, Chat)</li>\r\n<li>Virtual Retail</li>\r\n<li>Digital (T-Life app &amp; Site B.com)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr><tr><th width=\"20%\">Device purchase</th>\r\n<td width=\"80%\"><p><b>Samsung:</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><b><a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-s26.html\">Galaxy S26</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-s26-plus.html\">Galaxy S26+</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-s26-ultra.html\">Galaxy S26 Ultra</a></b></li>\r\n<li><b><a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-s25.html\">Galaxy S25</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-s25-plus.html\">Galaxy S25+</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-s25-ultra.html\">Galaxy S25 Ultra</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-s25-edge.html\">Galaxy S25 Edge</a>, <a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-s25-fe.html\">Galaxy S25 FE</a></b></li>\r\n<li><b><a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-z-flip7.html\">Galaxy Z Flip7,</a>&nbsp;<a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-z-fold7.html\">Galaxy Z Fold7</a></b></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-a37-5g.html\"><b>Galaxy A37</b></a></li>\r\n<li><a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/devices/phone/samsung-galaxy-xcover7-pro.html\"><b>Galaxy XCover7 Pro</b></a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Must purchase on&nbsp;EIP</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr><tr><th>New line activation</th>\r\n<td><p><b>New voice line required</b></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Lines added to the account via Change of Responsibility (COR) or BAN-to-BAN moves, converted from NCC/SCNC to normal Postpaid, and lines resumed from cancel do not qualify for this requirement.</li>\r\n<li>If a customer canceled a voice line within the past 90 days (excluding CORs and No Installs), the line must be resumed before they can add a brand-new voice line to qualify.</li>\r\n<li>TFB accounts cannot exceed 12 voice lines before taking advantage of this promotion. After qualifying lines have been enrolled, the customer may add additional lines to the account and exceed the 12 voice line limit.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr><tr><th width=\"20%\">Rate plan</th>\r\n<td width=\"80%\"><p><b>Plan / Feature from&nbsp;</b><a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/promotions/soc-groups/soc-group-69.html\"><b>SOC Group #69</b></a><b>&nbsp;required.</b></p>\r\n<p>Check the eligibility of specific plan SOCs at the top of the page.&nbsp;</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr><tr><th width=\"20%\">Trade-in</th>\r\n<td width=\"80%\">Not required</td>\r\n</tr><tr><th width=\"20%\">Port-in</th>\r\n<td width=\"80%\">Not required</td>\r\n</tr><tr><th width=\"20%\">Combinability</th>\r\n<td width=\"80%\"><ul>\r\n<li>Family Freedom:&nbsp;<b>YES</b>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>BreakFree or Keep and Switch: <b>NO</b></li>\r\n<li>RDC promos on the same EIP: <b>NO</b></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr><tr><th width=\"20%\">Not available for</th>\r\n<td width=\"80%\"><ul>\r\n<li>Contractor / Dealer accounts</li>\r\n<li>Site B for Business 13+ voice line accounts&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Certified Pre-Owned (CPO) device purchases</li>\r\n<li>Full Retail Price (FRP) purchases<br>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>JUMP!&nbsp; upgrades</li>\r\n<li>Standard upgrades on existing lines</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr><tr><th width=\"20%\">Payout</th>\r\n<td width=\"80%\"><p>Receive the promo value of $900 (approximately $37.50 per month) in 24 monthly&nbsp;<a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/promotions/promotion-handling/recurring-device-credits-rdc.html\">Recurring Device Credits (RDC)</a></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Promo value will not exceed the price of the purchased device.</li>\r\n<li>Credits begin within two bill cycles of qualification and last the length of the EIP term.</li>\r\n<li>Customers&nbsp;who enroll in a device promotion must maintain line of service and EIP tied to the promotion to receive the full value of the promo. If either is closed or canceled, the monthly credits will stop.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr></tbody></table>\r\n",
              "hideCaption": "false",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Tue May 19 2026 01:59:58 GMT+0000",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/table",
              "textIsRich": "true"
            }
          },
          "container_1693305467_1121746770": {
            "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
