            "title": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "jcr:createdBy": "Ashwini.PreethiP1@Site B.com",
              "jcr:title": "Review & take action",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "Ashwini.PreethiP1@Site B.com",
              "textStyle": "tdds:text-title-2",
              "isAccessRestricted": "false",
              "colorTextSource": "default",
              "jcr:created": "Wed Aug 28 2024 19:09:22 GMT+0000",
              "type": "h2",
              "linkTarget": "_self",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Wed Aug 28 2024 19:09:22 GMT+0000",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/title",
              "colorTextPalette": "tdds:color-primary-100",
              "colorText": "color-initial",
              "textAlignment": "tdds:ta-inherit"
            },
            "text": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "jcr:createdBy": "Epcy.Zacharias1@Site B.com",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "Alkia.Morris@Site B.com",
              "textStyle": "tdds:text-inherit",
              "marginTop": "tdds:mt-0",
              "isAccessRestricted": "false",
              "colorTextSource": "default",
              "jcr:created": "Wed Aug 28 2024 19:18:44 GMT+0000",
              "contentToggle": "false",
              "marginBottom": "tdds:mb-0",
              "text": "<ol>\r\n<li>Go over the promo&nbsp;details and these advisements with your customer so they understand what to do to get and keep this promo:<p>&nbsp;<span class=\"checkbox\">You'll receive the promo value as 24 monthly credits. These credits may begin within your 1-2 bill cycles after purchase. If you don't see a credit on your first bill, don't worry. You'll see a double credit on your second bill.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span class=\"checkbox\">Your promotional credits will be paid out for the full term of the EIP with no means to speed up their payout. Additionally, you must maintain the line of service and the EIP tied to the promotion to receive the full value of the promo. If either is closed or canceled, the monthly credits will stop.&nbsp;If you have a larger down payment, you may see a second bill credit with the same description on your bill. We apply this second bill credit to make up the difference for your higher out of pocket expense when your required down payment is greater than the promo value.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>Confirm customer is on or changing to a&nbsp;qualifying rate plan.&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>Help customers place their order.&nbsp;<ul>\r\n<li><b>Important:</b>&nbsp;The new phone EIP must be associated with the new&nbsp;activation.</li>\r\n<li>For ship-to orders, verify the correct email address is entered and remind customers they&nbsp;<i>MUST</i>&nbsp;sign their EIP agreement within 48 hours, or their order will be canceled.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><b>Retail:</b>&nbsp;Do&nbsp;<i>NOT</i>&nbsp;call the RSL to request Temp Double of the customer’s available ECL to make the customer eligible for the promo&nbsp;. These requests will be denied. Review <a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/operations/in-store/operational/store-issue-resolution-and-support.html\">Store issue resolution and support&nbsp;</a>before engaging RSL for additional support.</p>\r\n<p><b>Micro</b>:&nbsp;Digital Checkout must be created and accepted within the promo period to qualify.</p>\r\n",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Mon May 18 2026 21:45:29 GMT+0000",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/text",
              "colorTextPalette": "tdds:color-primary-100",
              "textIsRich": [
                "true",
                "true"
              ],
              "colorText": "color-initial",
              "textAlignment": "tdds:ta-inherit"
            }
          },
