              "colorTextSource": "default",
              "jcr:created": "Wed Aug 28 2024 19:23:10 GMT+0000",
              "contentToggle": "false",
              "marginBottom": "tdds:mb-0",
              "text": "<ul>\r\n<li>Customers can find the<b>&nbsp;Promo code</b>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<b>Bill name</b> on their bill statement.</li>\r\n<li>This promo is for a limited time only and subject to change and should be communicated to customers in this way.</li>\r\n<li><b>All qualification details must be clearly and accurately communicated with customers to ensure they understand the promotional eligibility requirements.</b></li>\r\n<li>Never add additional lines or features without the customer's consent.</li>\r\n<li>Promo available in NBA.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Fri Feb 06 2026 18:40:50 GMT+0000",
