            "accordion_copy_copy": {
              "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
              "jcr:createdBy": "nicole.hogan@Site B.com",
              "headingElement": "h3",
              "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "Alkia.Morris@Site B.com",
              "isAccessRestricted": "false",
              "hasDivider": "false",
              "jcr:created": "Fri Apr 18 2025 16:55:14 GMT+0000",
              "jcr:lastModified": "Mon May 18 2026 20:17:04 GMT+0000",
              "singleExpansion": "false",
              "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/accordion",
              "isInverse": "false",
              "isSplit": "false",
              "item_1744996206822": {
                "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
                "cq:panelTitle": "Demo Heading D",
                "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "nicole.hogan@Site B.com",
                "textStyle": "tdds:text-inherit",
                "marginTop": "tdds:mt-0",
                "isAccessRestricted": "false",
                "colorTextSource": "default",
                "contentToggle": "false",
                "marginBottom": "tdds:mb-0",
                "text": "<p>Customers shouldn't cancel an existing line with the intention of replacing it with a newly activated line to take advantage of this promo, even if the cancellation happens after the new line activation.</p>\r\n<p>Customers should never be told to cancel lines, before or after a promotion, in an effort to qualify or justify a promotion. If customers do not need additional lines, explore other promotions or discuss device price points. Driving CHURN to close sales is not the right thing to do.</p>\r\n",
                "jcr:lastModified": "Fri Apr 18 2025 17:14:36 GMT+0000",
                "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/text",
                "colorTextPalette": "tdds:color-primary-100",
                "textIsRich": [
                  "true",
                  "true"
                ],
                "colorText": "color-initial",
                "textAlignment": "tdds:ta-inherit"
              },
              "item_1744996211359": {
                "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
                "cq:panelTitle": "Demo Heading F",
                "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "nicole.hogan@Site B.com",
                "textStyle": "tdds:text-inherit",
                "marginTop": "tdds:mt-0",
                "isAccessRestricted": "false",
                "colorTextSource": "default",
                "contentToggle": "false",
                "marginBottom": "tdds:mb-0",
                "text": "<p>Yes, the new phone's EIP must be associated with the new line activated for this promo in order to qualify.</p>\r\n",
                "jcr:lastModified": "Fri Apr 18 2025 17:15:11 GMT+0000",
                "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/text",
                "colorTextPalette": "tdds:color-primary-100",
                "textIsRich": [
                  "true",
                  "true"
                ],
                "colorText": "color-initial",
                "textAlignment": "tdds:ta-inherit"
              },
              "item_1744996240605": {
                "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
                "cq:panelTitle": "Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet.",
                "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "nicole.hogan@Site B.com",
                "textStyle": "tdds:text-inherit",
                "marginTop": "tdds:mt-0",
                "isAccessRestricted": "false",
                "colorTextSource": "default",
                "contentToggle": "false",
                "marginBottom": "tdds:mb-0",
                "text": "<p>No. As long as the TFB customers are already enrolled in the promotion <i>BEFORE </i>adding the additional lines to their account, the account will continue to receive this promotion on the lines already enrolled.</p>\r\n",
                "jcr:lastModified": "Fri Apr 18 2025 17:16:45 GMT+0000",
                "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/text",
                "colorTextPalette": "tdds:color-primary-100",
                "textIsRich": [
                  "true",
                  "true"
                ],
                "colorText": "color-initial",
                "textAlignment": "tdds:ta-inherit"
              },
              "item_1744996261219": {
                "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
                "cq:panelTitle": "Demo Heading D",
                "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "Alkia.Morris@Site B.com",
                "textStyle": "tdds:text-inherit",
                "marginTop": "tdds:mt-0",
                "isAccessRestricted": "false",
                "colorTextSource": "default",
                "contentToggle": "false",
                "marginBottom": "tdds:mb-0",
                "text": "<p>Customers can only have one RDC promo attached to an active EIP. They may have multiple RDCs on the same line if they are attached to separate EIPs.</p>\r\n<p>Check <a href=\"/content/demo/us/en/customer-support/promotions/promotion-handling/recurring-device-credits-rdc.html\">Recurring Device Credits (RDC)</a> for more details on multiple RDCs on the same line.</p>\r\n",
                "jcr:lastModified": "Fri Feb 06 2026 18:43:33 GMT+0000",
                "sling:resourceType": "demo/components/proxy/content/text",
                "colorTextPalette": "tdds:color-primary-100",
                "textIsRich": [
                  "true",
                  "true"
                ],
                "colorText": "color-initial",
                "textAlignment": "tdds:ta-inherit"
              },
              "item_1744996281924": {
                "jcr:primaryType": "nt:unstructured",
                "cq:panelTitle": "Demo Heading E",
                "jcr:lastModifiedBy": "nicole.hogan@Site B.com",
                "textStyle": "tdds:text-inherit",
                "marginTop": "tdds:mt-0",
                "isAccessRestricted": "false",
                "colorTextSource": "default",
                "contentToggle": "false",
                "marginBottom": "tdds:mb-0",
                "text": "<p>Customers who enroll in a device promotion need to maintain the line of service and EIP tied to the promotion to receive the full value of their promo, but if either is closed or canceled, the monthly credits will stop.&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
                "jcr:lastModified": "Fri Apr 18 2025 17:24:44 GMT+0000",
